=Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Text Table=

This page documents the text encoding used in Dragon Warrior IV (US version).

==Overview==

Dragon Warrior IV uses a custom character encoding for all in-game text. The encoding is single-byte, with special control codes for text formatting.

